{"tid":2166573,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"報道：蒙牛被澳洲政府反對收購建議","createTime":"2020-08-20T13:34:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T13:46:14.000Z","uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6aa5a4c57b4854ca82afae3b8ac0669620cb7ad8","tid":2166573,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T13:34:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544832-20200820.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544832-20200820.htm&d=hRZI3RxrLdWDWG%2FiPctn5Tk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=2615e4ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544832-20200820.htm&h=4ae37101\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544832-20200820.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n澳洲傳媒報道，澳洲政府不會批准蒙牛乳業，向日本麒麟集團收購澳洲乳品及飲品公司Lion-Dairy&amp;Drinks。<br />\n<br />\n蒙牛去年11月提出收購建議，涉及逾30億港元。澳洲金融評論報引述消息人士指，收購已得到外商投資審核委員會（FIRB）批准，但澳洲財政部長弗呂登貝格反對。他並未有對報道作出評論。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲6月就外國投資法案，作出半世紀以來最大修訂，規定交易即使獲FIRB批准，財政部長仍有最終決定權，可要求更改交易、附帶條件或強制分拆，如果政府認為會對國家安全構成威脅，更可強制出售某家企業。<br />\n<br />\n中澳關係因新型肺炎疫情、港區國安法等而變得緊張，中國近日對澳洲進口大麥徵收關稅，暫停部份澳洲牛肉進口等。"},{"pid":"7b5f518de7bad981c92d1d051db4303f0b8ecd2d","tid":2166573,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T13:46:14.000Z","msg":"CLS <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uRctyX9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuRctyX9.gif&h=7315f061&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}